| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3462 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bb50cefa-edb8-57d0-b386-bc31fffc4b62"
